title: 'There's going to be a lot of death' in US from coronavirus next week, Trump says
description: White House experts forecast between 100,000 and 240,000 Americans could be killed in the pandemic even if orders to stay home are followed, as US President Donald Trump warns of a big spike in coronavirus fatalities in the coming days.
content:
Posted 
April 05, 2020 10:40:25
US President Donald Trump has told Americans "there's going to be a lot of death" due to coronavirus in the coming days, as the country braces for what he called the toughest two weeks of the pandemic.
